<li id="cite_note-Implications-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Implications_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Implications_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Implications_39-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCampbell1995" class="citation journal cs1">Campbell, Douglas (Fall 1995). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdf/45226110.pdf">"Changes in LDS Hymns: Implications and Opportunities"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought">Dialogue</a></i>. <b>28</b> (3). <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>: 65–91. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F45226110">10.2307/45226110</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/45226110">45226110</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:254298505">254298505</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue&amp;rft.atitle=Changes+in+LDS+Hymns%3A+Implications+and+Opportunities&amp;rft.ssn=fall&amp;rft.volume=28&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=65-91&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A254298505%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F45226110%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp