<li id="cite_note-107"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-107">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFShirley_Ann_Wilson_Moore2016" class="citation book cs1">Shirley Ann Wilson Moore (October 20, 2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=7xUkDQAAQBAJ"><i>Sweet Freedom's Plains: African Americans on the Overland Trails, 1841–1869</i></a>. Norman, Oklahoma: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Oklahoma_Press" title="University of Oklahoma Press">University of Oklahoma Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-8061-5686-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8061-5686-6"><bdi>978-0-8061-5686-6</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Sweet+Freedom%27s+Plains%3A+African+Americans+on+the+Overland+Trails%2C+1841%E2%80%931869&amp;rft.place=Norman%2C+Oklahoma&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Oklahoma+Press&amp;rft.date=2016-10-20&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8061-5686-6&amp;rft.au=Shirley+Ann+Wilson+Moore&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D7xUkDQAAQBAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANative+American+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
