<li id="cite_note-identity-112"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-identity_112-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-identity_112-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBennion2012" class="citation journal cs1">Bennion, Michael Kay (August 1, 2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://digitalscholarship.unlv.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2656&amp;context=thesesdissertations">"Captivity, Adoption, Marriage and Identity: Native American Children in Mormon Homes, 1847–1900"</a>. <i>UNLV Theses, Dissertations, Professional Papers, and Capstones</i>. <a href="/wiki/University_of_Nevada,_Las_Vegas" title="University of Nevada, Las Vegas">University of Nevada, Las Vegas</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171012032226/http://digitalscholarship.unlv.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2656&amp;context=thesesdissertations">Archived</a> from the original on October 12, 2017<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">October 12,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=UNLV+Theses%2C+Dissertations%2C+Professional+Papers%2C+and+Capstones&amp;rft.atitle=Captivity%2C+Adoption%2C+Marriage+and+Identity%3A+Native+American+Children+in+Mormon+Homes%2C+1847%E2%80%931900&amp;rft.date=2012-08-01&amp;rft.aulast=Bennion&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael+Kay&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalscholarship.unlv.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D2656%26context%3Dthesesdissertations&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANative+American+people+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
